## Quick Reference: Auto-stored Variables by createSHPFDraftOrderthoughAPI

The framework auto-stores these — do NOT add redundant `store_*` expressions:
- `<TEST_ID>shopifyOrderId` — Shopify order ID
- `<TEST_ID>shopifyOrderNumber` — Order number (without #)
- `<TEST_ID>customerId` — Shopify customer ID
- `<TEST_ID>customerFirstName` / `customerLastName`
- `<TEST_ID>lineItem1`, `lineItem2`, ... — Line item IDs
- `<TEST_ID>lineItemQty1`, `lineItemQty2`, ... — Line item quantities
- `<TEST_ID>shippingCost` — Shipping cost (if shipping lines exist)
